"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-27-beyonce-introduces-team-usa-at-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  American singer, Beyonc\\u00e9 made a surprise appearance during the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony broadcast on NBC Friday night, as she introduced several American athletes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999175458429579, \"rank\": 4.219390529849055e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.639115156815824e-22, \"text\": \"Beyonc\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\"}, {\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9949134546982273, \"rank\": 0.005112392899043108, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999175458429579, \"rank\": 4.219390529849055e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 'Drunk In Love' hitmaker donned a red, white and blue ensemble, including a 'USA' leotard and a billowing cape, along with cowboy boots and a cowboy hat.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.97082354767458, \"rank\": 0.030052634755209383, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Get a look at America, you all,\\\" Beyonce began, as her hit song 'Ya Ya' from her most recent album, 'Cowboy Carter,' played in the background.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9677193990223766, \"rank\": 0.03134468786926059, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These hopes and dreams, these superstars that represent us.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The people of this big, bold, beautiful, complicated nation.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rooting together for them.\\\"\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She shouted out a few members of the team - Simone Biles, Sha'Carri Richardson, Noah Lyles, Caeleb Dressel, and Katie Ledecky.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}, {\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That pride and that joy?\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what gets me about this team.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what makes me believe in this team.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's why I can not wait to see what they pull off over these next 16 days.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"America, give it up for Team U.S.A., the very best of who we are.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9999983666968697, \"rank\": 1.6333058081826353e-06, \"text\": \"Team U.S.A.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a vision to behold.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a team to believe in.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a night to celebrate,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Extremely disrespectful' - Elon Musk slams Drag Queen's parody of Last Supper at Paris Olympics  'I am honoured' - Celine Dion relishes comeback performance at Paris Olympics opening ceremony  Beyonce get stuck mid air as her flying car suffers technical mishap [VIDEO]  Beyonc\\u00e9, Jay-Z contemplating legal action against Kanye West over disturbing remarks  Kendrick Lamar breaks Beyonc\\u00e9's record on Billboard charts  Beyonc\\u00e9 said she's done with acting - Mother, Tina Knowles reveals  Grammys: Beyonc\\u00e9 earns her first ever win for 'Album of the Year', extends record as most awarded  Beyonc\\u00e9 becomes most RIAA certified female artist of all time  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd